        <li><a href="#installer">Important: Run the UltraLite-mk3 Software Installer First</a></li>
        <li><a href="#hardware">Installing the UltraLite-mk3 Hybrid Hardware (excerpt)</a></li>
        <li><a href="#cuemix">CueMix FX (verbatim)</a></li>
        <li><a href="#frontpanel">Front-panel Operation — LCD modes & menus (verbatim)</a></li>
        <li><a href="#channel-page">Channel Page Parameters (excerpt)</a></li>
